											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="A dark aura pulses from the black mirror, casting shadows throughout the chamber. Shadowheart doubles over in pain as her incurable wound flares intensely. Her parents also writhe in agony. Finally it abates and Shadowheart straightens - to see a vast silhouette of Shar leaning over her and her parents. Shar's features cannot be clearly seen, but her words reverberate through SH's head." />
